{"type": "article", "id": 16156, "title": "“now and then”展览", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-16T06:50:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 59, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115212njKecIbCoGEYlvaD.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是建筑师兼设计师 Natascha Madeiski 和银器匠兼珠宝匠  Linnie Mclarty 的跨界合作。他们分别制作陶瓷容器和金属配件，并巧妙结合成“now and then”的展览。复古造型的陶瓷容器配上有未来感的金属作手柄和勺子显得很独特，似乎保留了物件的大致轮廓，点缀的地方仍然是现代的，是他们向历史和建筑的致敬。容器有灰、粉、绿、白四种颜色和四种造型，它们的展示也像是考古的切面。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143511ZF4c2HINdvByi83P.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143512xS7ebMEaowt29OjV.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143513pP8tzMlU4hQZqo5D.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"1129\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.3801956\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016072614351487rTgkNZ0ReWXHtF.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143514rijl19BS2CAWQzkc.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}